cast.overview: A five-year-old Indian boy gets lost on the streets of Calcutta, thousands of kilometers from home. He survives many challenges before being adopted by a couple in Australia; 25 years later, he sets out to find his lost family.
cast.title: Lion

details.biography: Priyanka Bose is an Indian film actress and model. Active on stage and in films, she is best known for her role in the Italian film Gangor among others. Priyanka started her film career with small roles in Love Sex aur Dhokha, Sorry Bhai!, Johnny Gaddar and Guzaarish.
details.name: Priyanka Bose
